<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Rules" content-collection-id="NYCrules" source-infobase-title="The Rules of the City of New York" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\NYCrules.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCrules_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCrules_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-84522" number="99179" version="2186">
			<HEADING>Chapter 8: Petitions for Rulemaking</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17414" name="T48C008"/>Chapter 8: Petitions for Rulemaking</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-131757" number="99180" version="2186">
								<HEADING>§ 8-01 Scope.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17416" name="T48C008_8-01"/>§ 8-01 Scope.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131756" number="99181" version="2497">
									<PARA>These rules govern the procedures by which the public may submit to the Office of Administrative Trials and Hearings (OATH) petitions for rulemaking, pursuant to Section <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="1043" destination-id="0-0-0-0">1043</LINK>(g) of the New York City Charter (City Administrative Procedure Act), and the procedures for OATH&apos;s consideration and disposition of such petitions. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131755" number="99182" version="2186">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 1/10/2022, eff. 2/9/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-131760" number="99183" version="2186">
								<HEADING>§ 8-02 Definitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17418" name="T48C008_8-02"/>§ 8-02 Definitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131754" number="99184" version="2186">
									<PARA>As used in this chapter: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131753" number="99185" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">City Administrative Procedure Act.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;City Administrative Procedure Act&quot; means the requirements for rulemaking by agencies of the City of New York specified in <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="Chapter 45" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Chapter 45</LINK> of the New York City Charter. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131752" number="99186" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Commissioner.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Commissioner&quot; means OATH&apos;s Chief Administrative Law Judge and Chairperson of the Environmental Control Board. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131751" number="99187" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Person.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Person&quot; means an individual, partnership, corporation, or other legal entity, and any individual or entity acting in a fiduciary or representative capacity. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131750" number="99188" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Petition.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Petition&quot; means a request that OATH adopt a rule. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131749" number="99189" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Petitioner.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Petitioner&quot; means the person who files a petition. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131748" number="99190" version="2502">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Rule.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Rule&quot; has the same meaning as in Section <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="1813066185-672468487-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Charter.NFO" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="1041" destination-id="0-0-0-0">1041</LINK>(5) of the New York City Charter. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131747" number="99191" version="2186">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 1/10/2022, eff. 2/9/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-131759" number="99192" version="2186">
								<HEADING>§ 8-03 Procedures for Submitting Petitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17420" name="T48C008_8-03"/>§ 8-03 Procedures for Submitting Petitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131746" number="99193" version="2186">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Any person may petition the Commissioner to adopt a rule. The petition must include: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131745" number="99194" version="2186">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The proposed language of the rule; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131744" number="99195" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Petitioner&apos;s arguments in support of adoption of the rule; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131743" number="99196" version="2497">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(3)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The name, address, telephone number, and e-mail address of the petitioner or the petitioner&apos;s authorized representative; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131742" number="99197" version="2186">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(4)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The signature of petitioner or his or her representative. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131741" number="99198" version="2186">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Any change in the information provided pursuant to paragraph three of subdivision (a) of this section must be reported promptly in writing to OATH by (1) mail to OATH at 66 John Street, 11th Floor, New York, N.Y. 10038, ATTN: General Counsel; or (2) e-mail to Rules_Oath@oath.nyc.gov. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131740" number="99199" version="2186">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 1/10/2022, eff. 2/9/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-131758" number="99200" version="2186">
								<HEADING>§ 8-04 Procedures for Consideration of and Responses to Petitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17422" name="T48C008_8-04"/>§ 8-04 Procedures for Consideration of and Responses to Petitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131739" number="99201" version="2186">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>When a petition submitted in proper form is received, the Commissioner, or his or her representative, will deny or approve the petition within 60 days from the date the petition was received. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131738" number="99202" version="2186">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Commissioner, or his or her representative, will either deny the petition in a written statement or grant the petition by stating in writing his or her intention to initiate rulemaking by a specified date. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131737" number="99203" version="2186">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Commissioner, or his or her representative, may grant the petition in whole or in part and is not bound by the proposed language in the petition. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131736" number="99204" version="2186">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Commissioner, or his or her representative, may amend or modify the language of the rule as proposed in the petition at his or her discretion. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-131734" number="99205" version="2186">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 1/10/2022, eff. 2/9/2022) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-069]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>